archimate:BusinessProcess.name: Assign Value to Configuration Parameter
archimate:BusinessProcess.documentation: Assign a value to a configuration parameter.

properties.value: Assign Value to Configuration Parameter assigns a value to a configuration parameter as defined by parameters that are part of a selected configuration specification. Note that this process also uses a generalized set of processes to assign a value to the parameter and to create any inter-value relationships, called characteristic values. To date the generic processes have not yet been developed.
